          "component_id": "textual_research",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "artifactPos": "",
                "desc": "<p><strong>Message</strong></p><p>\"Hey, you! Yeah, you, the one reading this message.\"</p><p>\"Add 'just like love' at the end of any sentence, and it will sound wise.\"</p><p>\"Take my motto, for example...\"</p><p>\"Hard work is all there is to the craft! Just like love!\"<br><br><strong>Cat's Tail's reply</strong></p><p>Cat's Tail is always here for you, no matter when! Just like love!</p>",
